Name: Chit Chat
Description: Hey adventurer!  Since this is your first quest, talk to [n4] to learn more!

Name: Convenient Collection
Description: [n2] is working on a cool project but needs a couple items to complete it.  Bring him 3 [i10205], 3 [i10206] and 3 [i10211].

Name: Spread the Word
Description:
Place a [i814] in each of the 5 locations around the lake. You will know the correct location because that area will be surrounded by sparkles. 
Go back and talk to [n211] when you're done!

Name: Missing Pieces
Description:
Help [n221] find the missing band equipment. He's looking for these items: 2 [i815]s, [i816] and [i817].
Once you find all of the items bring them back to [n221]. Look around the Dream Carnival for these items.

Name: The Wandering Wand
Description: [n218] is looking for [n219] who has her wand. Find [n219] somewhere in the carnival, get [n218]'s wand back and return it to her.

Name: Something's Stir Frying
Description: [n215] wants to teach you how to cook but first she'll need a couple of ingredients: 3 [i10215]s, 2 [i10256]s, 1 [i10257] and 1 [i10254]. You can get the [i10215] by harvesting Eggplants in your farm while the rest can be purchased from the [n265]. Bring these ingredients to [n215] when you're done collecting them all.

Name: All Time Favorite
Description: [n215] found out that [n216]'s craving [i10219]. Unfortunately, she's all out of ingredients. She needs 3 [i10216]s, 2 [i10252], 1 [i10253], 1 [i10256] and 1 [i10254]. You can harvest [i10216]s from your farm while you can purchase everything else from the [n265]. Bring these ingredients to [n215]. She will then teach you how to make [i10219].

Name: Enjoy the Little Things
Description: [n221] is looking for crazy treasures scattered all over the [p15]. You need to find 1 [i824], 1 [i825], 1 [i826] and 1 [i827]. They could be anywhere in [p15] so keep your eyes peeled!

Name: Your End of the Deal
Description: [n212] and [n220] made a deal that involved trading a box full of knick-knacks. However, [n220] still hasn't given his end of the deal yet and [n212] is getting worried. He needs you to take [i828] and bring it to [n220].

Name: The Great Cover-Up
Description: [n220] hasn't collected the things he promised [n212] because he's having too much fun in the [p15]. He needs your help to collect 8 [i10211] from Vibrant Deposit and 4 [i10193] from the [m234] that can be found in the Adventure Area. Return to [n220] when you've collected everything.

Name: The Pet Necessities
Description: Pets are awesome friends and now's your chance to play and interact with them! If you right click on a pet, you can either pet them or feed them. Petting increases a pet's happiness while feeding them prevents hunger. A hungry pet is a sad pet and you don't want that to happen to your cherished companion. Pet food is easy to find since the [n229] sells it. Now that you know the basics of pet care, talk to [n217] again.

Name: Hanamaru's Bankaroo
Description: [n282] needs help with math. Play Bankaroo and flex your numeric muscles!

Name: Badtz-Maru Homerun Derby
Description: Batter up! Guide [n220]'s aim and hit the right ball. Knock it out of the park!

Name: A Friend In Me
Description: Welcome to the [p15]! Before you enter, [n213] recommends that you bring with you one of the [p15] Guardians. These loyal friends will clue you in on the different things going on in the [p15]. You can choose one of the three: [n260], [n261] and [n262]. Remember, don't complete the quest if you're still unsure about which Guardian to use.

Name: Chewppies Acorn Catch
Description: The Chewppies are playing "Acorn Catch". However they need your help to organize who is catching the acorns. They really, really love the acorns so help them out!

Name: Melody's Cookie Cluster
Description: Are you ready to bake cookies with [n217]? Melody's Cookie Cluster is quite simple: Pull cookies out of the dish and put them in the oven. Line up 3 cookies of the same kind horizontally or vertically to cook them. Don't let the cookies pile up too much!

Name: Okigaru Friends Hide and Seek
Description: The Okigaru friends are up to their playful ways again. They want to play hide and seek with you. Test your memory skills as they shuffle all over the place.

Name: Scavenger Hunt
Description: Find the 30 [i10268]s scattered around the Dream Carnival fairgrounds! Return to [n236] when you are done.

Name: Get The Ball Rolling
Description: The [n289] wants to challenge your minigame skill. Each of the 3 [n282]s located in the Harbour section of the [p15] will let you play different minigames. Talk to [n289] again to begin the challenge.

Name: Follow the Sparkly Path
Description: It's now time for you to explore more of the [p15]. He laid out [i10292] for you to follow. Collect each one and follow the trail!

Name: Farming 101
Description: The [n275] is feeling a little generous. He wants you to put the 3 [i10260], 3 [i10261] and 3 [i10065] to good use. Farming is fun, so try it out!

Name: Lazy Snakey
Description: [n236] is looking for the 3 [n286]s. They are probably in their hiding places right now. Their only job in the [p15] is to let its visitors play more minigames. Find them and wake them up so you can play the minigames. Also, remember that the [n286]s hid the path to their hiding place well. Find the path to get to them! Once they're all awake, return to [n236]. After returning to [n236], you can access the minigames from the [n286]s.

Name: Angry Charging Rhinos
Description: See if you can get a [i10198] from one of the [m104]s on the adventure area. It won't be easy!

Name: The Dream Carnival
Description: [n221] by the [p15] entrance welcomes you! He suggests speaking to [n213] so you can get your very own guardian.

Name: Back to You
Description: [n211] wants to return the favor to [n221] by laying out another trail of [i10292]. Collect each one and follow the trail!

Name: It Must Be Good!
Description: With the materials you collected earlier, cook [i10219] and give one to [n216].

Name: The Return Trip
Description: Give [i829] to [n212].

Name: Freebies!
Description: [n273] is going to give you something special. Talk to him again to find out.

Name: Little Twin Stars Letter Express
Description: Help the Little Twin Stars' sort out the mail

Name: The Winner
Description: It's time to play minigames! Play and win at least one of the minigames: Badtz-Maru Homerun Derby, Little Twin Stars Letter Express, or Hanamaru Bankaroo. When you've won, you can either return to [n289] or play the other games and finish them successfully. The more minigames you finish, the better your prize is.

Name: The Winner
Description: It's time to play minigames! Play and win at least one of the minigames: Badtz-Maru Homerun Derby, Little Twin Stars Letter Express, or Hanamaru Bankaroo. When you've won, you can either return to [n289] or play the other games and finish them successfully. The more minigames you finish, the better your prize is.

Name: The Winner
Description: It's time to play minigames! Play and win at least one of the minigames: Badtz-Maru Homerun Derby, Little Twin Stars Letter Express, or Hanamaru Bankaroo. When you've won, you can either return to [n289] or play the other games and finish them successfully. The more minigames you finish, the better your prize is.

Name: Welcome to Sanrio Land!
Description:
Welcome to Sanrio Land, adventurer! Please go to 
[n20] to collect a set of dry clothing. [n20] is 
located in the southwestern area of [p8].

Name: Collecting Shamrock
Description:
[n20] needs [i1401] and [i1402] for his research on plants! He would like you to gather 12 [i1401] and 6 [i1402] right away. You will be able to find these in the southwestern area of [p8].
To collect [i1401] and [i1402], locate the Shamrock and then right click on it.

Name: A Favor for Pochacco
Description: [n104] has been looking for you! He is in need of some assistance. Make your way back to [p8] to see what he needs.

Name: A Star Ingredient!
Description: [n104] needs you to collect [i5003] and [i1203] for [n17]. The [i5003] can be found on [m2] on the eastern area of [p8] and the [i1203] can be chopped from Spiral Wood. Remember to equip the [i2039] [n104] gave you before you encounter the [m2]! [n17] can be found in the northeastern area of [p8].

Name: A Cooking Essential
Description: [n17]'s [i1755] needs something else to make it yummy. She thinks that 5 [i10132] and 5 [i10141] will add that much needed flavor for her [i1755]. Go to your farm and get her these crops or you can buy them from the [n26].

Name: To Warm Things Up
Description:
The soup is ready and [n17] would like you to 
deliver the soup to [n24] at the lighthouse. The 
lighthouse is located at southwestern area of [p8] by the shore.

Name: Learn to Cook
Description: [n24] would like you to purchase 3 [i1711], 2 [i1709], and 3 [i1702]. So he can make you a nice loaf of [i1710]! Visit [n26] in [p8] and pick up the ingredients! Bring it back to [n24] when you gathered all the ingredient. He's also craving for [i601]. You can ask [n21] about it.

Name: Clean-Up Crew
Description: [n21]'s farm is very, very messy and she needs your help cleaning it up. Go into her farm and pick up all the [i603] scattered all around.

Name: Ghosts in Sanrio Harbour
Description: [n21] thinks that ghosts are the cause of the missing crops. Pay her farm a visit and see what's really going and try to get 10 of [i602] back.

Name: Check Out The View
Description: [n21] is very proud of her fully-grown farm and wants you to take a look. Perhaps it can inspire you to start farming as well. Talk to [n21] again once you've visited her farm.

Name: Chocolate Goodness
Description: [n24] would like you to make [i1713] and deliver it to [n124]. You can find all the ingredients at the [n26].

Name: Trouble in Paradise
Description: The [i1713] is a nice touch for [n124] but he is still a little down because his surfboard broke. Can you help him make a new surfboard? He needs [i1203], [i5003], [i1401] and [i1825]. You can purchase the [i8406] from the [n26].

Name: The Story Begins
Description:
[n124] discovered a mysterious box while surfing. He would like you to bring it to [n21] and see would he know anything about this item. [n21] 
is located across of [p82].

Name: Conquering the Waves
Description:
[n124] is very excited about his new surfboard and 
he would like to take it out for a spin. He would like 
you to go with him and help keep an eye out for obstacles in his way!

Name: A Great Discovery
Description: [n21] opened the box and found a top hat, bow tie and key with a picture of [n112]. She is convinced that the key will open [p82]. Make your way to [p82] in the middle of [p8] to learn more about this.

Name: A Hungry Penguin
Description:
[n112] is hungry! VERY VERY HUNGRY! In his 
weakened state, he won't be able to help you. Go and gather fish by the pond and then come back to [n112].

Name: Mystery Revealed
Description: Now that [n112] is awake, he would like you to go check on [n37] and the gang in [p9]. Head north of [p8] and you will find the pathway to [p9]. Check in with [n28] to see how is everyone doing in [p9]!

Name: Return the Books
Description:
[n25] is worried that [n16], [n18] and [n19] will 
forget to return the books on time, so she's asking 
you to remind them. They are just near the port. 
Don't go too far away!

Name: A Wise Choice
Description:
[n18] and [n19] are thinking about what they should 
have for dinner. [n18] wants hamburgers but 
[n19] wants sandwiches. Can you help them 
decide? 
Talk to [n18] if you think they should eat 
hamburgers or talk to [n19] if you think they should 
eat sandwich! Hurry!!

Name: Beautiful Flowers
Description:
[n25] loves the [i1403] by the [p8] Pond! 
She would like you to collect some for her. Bring 10 [i1403] and return it to [n25]. 
The [i1403] is located in the Center of [p8].

Name: A New Plant??
Description:
While collecting flowers for [n25], you have discovered some [i1404]. [n25] is very interested 
in these leaves and would like you to collect 10
samples for her to research. [i1404] can be collected from the Dark Opal Basil by the center of [p8].

Name: A Crabby Situation
Description:
[n16] wants to make [i514]s. In order to do so, he needs to gather some [i1004] from [m1]. However, he is having a hard time catching those tricky [m1]s. Can you help him gather 10 [i1004]? 
The [m1] is located near the [p8] Pond 
in the center of [p8].

Name: Just a Few Sticks Short
Description:
[n16] needs [i1201] to start a nice bonfire for 
tonight's bonfire gathering. He would like you to 
help him collect 10 [i1201] from the Bushes in the 
northwestern area of [p8].

Name: Magic Goodness!
Description:
[n19] would like some [i1798] for his party later on. 
However, he is out of [i1713] and would like you to 
make some for him. Bring back 5 [i1713] and he 
will teach you how to make [i1798].

Name: Sandwich for Your Thoughts
Description:
[n19] needs some [i1710] to make his special 
sandwich. If you craft 3 [i1710] for him. He will 
teach you the recipe for his [i1739].

Name: Welcome to Florapolis!
Description: Welcome to [p9]! Just as [n112] suspected, some people in [p9] have fallen asleep as well! [n28] has asked you to help him solve these mysteries. Go visit [n30] or [n23] to learn more about these slumbering characters.

Name: Finishing the Job
Description: Before [n36] fell into deep sleep, she was renovating her house with [n23]. Although she's still asleep, [n23] already started finishing the job they started together but he needs a healthy break. [i10131] and [i10118] would really hit the spot right now.

Name: Renovation Madness
Description: [n23] would like you to collect 3 [i5033] and 3 [i5080] and 5 [i1005] for [p205] renovation project! You can find these in the [p34] and [p35]. Return to [n23] after collecting these items.

Name: Good Deeds and Seeds
Description: [n28] is in need of farming supplies. Since everyone has fallen asleep, all deliveries of farming supplies to [p9] have stopped. However, there are a couple of folks in [p9] that own gardens. Perhaps you can ask them for some supplies. Visit [n29], [n32] and [n23] and ask them for help. Return to [n28] once you have the needed materials.

Name: Potato Rumble
Description:
It's time for you to learn how to farm. Here's what you do: 
First off, you'll need to fertilize the land. Each square on the farm can fit one plant so fertilize a square with the [i84], then plant something on it.
After seeds have been planted, they'll need to be watered with [i351]s every day. The icon you see on the top left whenever you're in your farm will tell you when each day starts and ends. When the icon is empty, it's the beginning of the day and when it's full it's the end of the day.
To harvest, all you do is right click on a plant and then click gather. [n28] needs you to harvest 15 [i10132] and give it to him.

Name: Yam-Tastic!
Description: While rummaging through his supplies, [n28] found a [i10131] recipe. He wants you to plant and harvest 15 [i10131] and 15 [i10108].

Name: Snappy Snap Peas
Description: [n28] is amazed at having found a [i10125] recipe - he really should be more tidy. He wants you to plant and harvest 20 [i10125] 20 [i10118].

Name: Returning the Favor
Description: [n28] never forgot the good people that helped him out with the farm supplies. He wants to return the favor by giving them crops grown from his farm. He wants you to give 5 [i10132] to [n29], 5 [i10131] to [n32] and 10 [i10125] to [n23]. Talk to [n28] again when you're done returning favors.

Name: Have a Break
Description: [n28] needs you to spread the joy of sharing. Make 8 [i1832] and give them out to all the folks in [p9]. You can purchase the [i8407] from one of the Merchants in [p9]. Return to him when you've handed out the delicious treats.

Name: Tool Trip
Description: [n23] needs your help once again! Please go to [p8] and pick up a [i570] from [n104]. Also you'll need to talk to [n124] and [n21] for [i587] and [i588].

Name: A Kind Act
Description: Thanks to you, [n23] is making great time for renovating [p205]! He would like to show his appreciation for you by making you something cool. Collect 5 [i1207], 5 [i1204], 5 [i5051], 2 [i5020] and 2 [i5021]. They can be found in [p31].

Name: A Prank Gone Wrong
Description: [i578] has gone missing! [n23] suspects it is [n32], [n135], [n25] and [n104] playing a prank. Help [n23] retrieve the following items: [i578], [i579], [i580], and [i581] from the culprits. You can find them around [p9] and [p8].

Name: Pearl All Around
Description: [n36] has one final challenge for you! She would like you to gather 6 [i1002], 6 [i1001] and 6 [i1825]. In return, she will teach you how to make [i17517] and give you [i12].

Name: Whose key it is?
Description: [n23] found a Mysterious Key that might be a clue needed to wake up [n36]. He would like you to go to [p205] and see what happens.

Name: Chop Chop!
Description: [n36] would like to make a [i25] for you! Go and collect 20 [i1209], 10 [i1210] and 2 [i514] and bring it back to [n36]. You can find the [i1209], and [i1210] on Kaolit from [p32] and [p33]. While [i514] needs to be crafted.

Name: Snip Snip!
Description: [n36] needs 5 [i1211], 10 [i1003] and 15 [i1204] to  make a pair of [i2]! Please go to the [p34] or [p35] to collect [i1003] and [p33] or [p32] to collect [i1211]. You will be able to find [i1204] in [p31].

Name: House-Building 101
Description:
Since [n36] still got some leftover materials from the renovation and she wants to give you a chance to build your own house with those materials! Talk to her again to get the house certificate and try to building it in your own farm! 
To build your house, simply right click on the House Certificate that [n36] gave you. You will then have to collect the necessary building materials for construction. House construction requires you to play a minigame and after you successfully finish a minigame, you have to complete the rest of the house by right clicking on it. Make sure you keep your Action Point up when finishing your house! Low-level houses only require you to play 1 minigames but as the houses get better, there will be more minigames for you to fiinish.

Name: Lost in the Forest
Description: [n33] is missing! The last time anyone saw him, he was looking for materials in the Dream Forests. Please go and investigate [p31], [p32] and [p33].

Name: Shelling Out
Description: [n33] is nowhere to be found and [n30] has been so busy worrying that she has fallen behind in her business. She needs you to gather 20 [i1001] for an order. [i1001] can be found from the Sea Rock in [p34] or [p35].

Name: Bug Hunt
Description: [n30] believes [n39] knows more about the missing [n33]. It is described here along with his order  forms for 10 [i1407]. Collect the [i1407] and deliver them to [n39]. [i1407] can be found on your farm's plants. They are also located on plants in [p36] and [p37].

Name: A Roll of the Dye
Description: [n33] is safe and sound at his house! He was collecting 10 [i1409], 5 [i1005] and 10 [i515] before he fell into this sudden slumber. [n39] would like to finish the job in hope the good deed will wake him up! Go and collect the [i1409] from [p36] and [p37], [i1005] from [p34] or [p35] and [i515] from the [n93].

Name: Stocking Up
Description: With the [i1814] crossed out on the list, the next items on the list are [i511], [i571] and [i510]! Go and collect 5 [i5013] from [m6] in [p33], 5 [i1205] from Bushes in [p8]. You also need to get 5 [i5009], 5 [i5021] and 5 [i5113] . [m5] and [m11] can be found in [p31] while [m7] can be found in [p32]. Return to [n39] once you have everything.

Name: Pass the Message!
Description: [n39] would like you to drop off some Invitations throughout [p8] and [p9]. Please give invitations to [n30] and [n32] in [p9] and [n20], [n16] and [n21] in [p8]. Return to [n39] once you do so.

Name: The Mystery Key
Description: You obtained a [i528]. Could this be the key that you and [n39] have been searching for? Please bring it back to [n39] for confirmation.

Name: A Clean Start
Description: The key is indeed [n33]'s key! However, it is very dirty and [n39] would like to clean it up before bringing it to [p203]. She needs you to collect 10 [i614] from the Kitty Lake in [p8]. Bring it to [n39] once you have it.

Name: The Lost Key
Description: With the key all clean and shiny, [n39] would like you to take it to [n33] who is sleeping in his house. Please hurry to [p203]. It is on the north side of [p9].

Name: Tailor in Training
Description: [n33] has woken up! Now he can get back to his day-to-day tasks. However, he needs your help. Please make him 2 [i1826] and 2 [i1827]. Return to [n33] upon acquiring these items.

Name: Tailor Made
Description: [n33] has woken up! Now he can get back to his day-to-day tasks. However, he needs your help. Make as much [i1826], [i1827], [i1828], [i1829] and [i16053]. Since some of these items are harder to make, bringing more of them will grant you a greater reward. You can purchase the [i8609] in [p9]. Return to [n33] upon acquiring these items.
